Pleiotropic action of MTHFD1 was studied. 16 quantitative markers were taken into account.

Quantitative markers: 
physiological: body mass index, diastolic blood pressure, forced expiratory volume in 1 second, heart rate, systolic blood pressure; 
blood: adiponectin, albumin in serum, blood glucose, creatinine, hemoglobin, high-density lipoprotein cholesterol, total cholesterol, triglycerides; 
and inflammation: albumin in urine, C-reactive protein, interleukin 6.
